  "detailed_description": "<h1>Build your way brick-by-brick through adventurous LEGO® dioramas!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>LEGO Brawls is an easy-pick-up, \"everybody-friendly\" platform brawler. Whether you're looking for a quick play casual battle, an unlockables grind, a competitive rank climb to the top of the global leaderboards, or even just creative brawler building, LEGO Brawls has something for you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/a9334d1dccd71717eb95fe20236c0512.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>Design your ultimate LEGO Minifigure hero with unique style, strategy and personality. With over 77 TRILLION combination possibilities, almost anything is possible. A cactus with an attitude? A scrappy janitor ninja who happens to have fighting chickens? A sledgehammer-swinging clown with a few scores to settle? Sure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.poster.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.webm?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.mp4?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/9882b9c4e0b75656e47581fcd632a3d1.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>From the swashbuckling shores of Barracuda Bay, to the waterlogged caverns of Ninjago Seabound, to a dusty wild west saloon and the mythical Monkie Kid jungle, all of your favorite LEGO themes are brawlable! Collect unlockable minifigures, power-ups, and emotes along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.poster.avif?t=1704236044\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.webm?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.mp4?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/bd353f1de7be69b27c04b3370f264993.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>Cross-play your friends across platforms! Team up and brawl 4v4, party with friends, or play a battle royale-style game mode where it’s “every-player-for-themself”. With multiple game modes, levels have unique challenges and win conditions.",
  "about_the_game": "LEGO Brawls is an easy-pick-up, \"everybody-friendly\" platform brawler. Whether you're looking for a quick play casual battle, an unlockables grind, a competitive rank climb to the top of the global leaderboards, or even just creative brawler building, LEGO Brawls has something for you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/a9334d1dccd71717eb95fe20236c0512.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>Design your ultimate LEGO Minifigure hero with unique style, strategy and personality. With over 77 TRILLION combination possibilities, almost anything is possible. A cactus with an attitude? A scrappy janitor ninja who happens to have fighting chickens? A sledgehammer-swinging clown with a few scores to settle? Sure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.poster.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.webm?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/818c79fd08a63816b7660ce3cf142ba8.mp4?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/9882b9c4e0b75656e47581fcd632a3d1.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>From the swashbuckling shores of Barracuda Bay, to the waterlogged caverns of Ninjago Seabound, to a dusty wild west saloon and the mythical Monkie Kid jungle, all of your favorite LEGO themes are brawlable! Collect unlockable minifigures, power-ups, and emotes along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.poster.avif?t=1704236044\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.webm?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/5dacd78b52155de2b5b3937cef6de2d7.mp4?t=1704236044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/bd353f1de7be69b27c04b3370f264993.avif?t=1704236044\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br>Cross-play your friends across platforms! Team up and brawl 4v4, party with friends, or play a battle royale-style game mode where it’s “every-player-for-themself”. With multiple game modes, levels have unique challenges and win conditions.",
